---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technology | Fluidity Marine">
	<main>
		<section id="tech-hero">
			<h1>Active Boundary Layer <span class="electric-text">Thrust Vectoring</span></h1>
			<p class="tagline">The end of mechanical rudders. The beginning of digital hydrodynamics.</p>
		</section>

		<section id="moat-grid">
			<div class="moat-card">
				<h2>01. Parasitic Drag Termination</h2>
				<p>By eliminating the rudder, we reclaim up to 12% of traditional propulsion energy lost to parasitic surface friction.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="moat-card">
				<h2>02. Transom Jet Array</h2>
				<p>A synchronized 7-node thrust interface allows for millisecond-precision yaw control through differential boundary layer modulation.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="moat-card">
				<h2>03. Zero External Moving Parts</h2>
				<p>Removing the #1 failure point in marine propulsion. No appendages to snag, break, or corrode below the waterline.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="cta">
			<a href="https://wefunder.com/fluidity" class="button primary">Become a Part Owner</a>
			<a href="/" class="button secondary">Back to Home</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		color: #e2e8f0;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.electric-text {
		background: linear-gradient(to right, #00f2fe, #4facfe);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}
	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #94a3b8;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}
	#moat-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}
	.moat-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}
	.moat-card h2 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #fff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	#cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	.button {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: transform 0.2s;
	}
	.button.primary {
		background: #fff;
		color: #050a0f;
	}
	.button.secondary {
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: #fff;
	}
	.button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
</style>
